Directed by Jashwant Gangani.

Written by Jashwant Gangani. Jashwant Gangani. Jashwant Gangani. Jashwant Gangani.

Cast Mugdha Godse(Suhani (credit only)). Sneha Ullal(Rumzum (credit only)). Nishant Malkani(Swagat (as Nishant) (credit only)). Darshan Jariwala(Rashmikant Patel). Farida Jalal(Savitri). Sachin Khedekar(Mansukh). Muni Jha(Vipul Shah). Smita Jaykar(Laxmi Shah). Alex Ashman(Liza).Jitu Pandya. Soniya Mehta(Ananya). Rittesh Mobh(Pintu). Akshita Sethi(Jassi). Aru Krishansh Verma(Parbat).Devendra Pandit.Sanjay Patel.Rakesh Pujara.Abhijeet.Saloni.Ajay Sharma.Hitesh Rawal.Yasmine Deliken.Naresh Patel. Rahul Sharma((as Dr. Rahul Sharma)).Gautam Shrivastav . Yasemin Delikan(Nikki)

Language Hindi.

Producers C.J.Gadara. Alex Anthony Fernandes. Jashwant Gangani. Raj Gangani. Dinesh Likhiya.

Production Gangani Motion Pictures.
